channel.description:
Kid Candy Reviews every Thursday, Time For Toys every Tuesday, every Friday is Kawaii Day!  Mini-movies, animation and more featuring sisters Jillian and Adelaide!  Subscribe today!

Babyteeth4 features sisters Jillian and Addie, age 10 and 8, in the number one candy review show in the world!  They are also well-known for their series of hilariously epic misadventures, such as "Too Many Addies" and "Fast Cars, Bad Kids".  

Produced by their father, their sweetly comic videos have entertained millions viewers around the world since 2008.  Jillian and Addie, Babyteeth4, have appeared on TV news and talk shows, the front page of a major newspaper, and a large market radio station.
